#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Kako začeti"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "When you start &kturtle; you will see something like this:"
msgstr "Ko zaženete &kturtle; videli boste nekaj takega:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: getting-started.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of &kturtle; when you start it for the first time"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kturtle; ko ga zaženete prvič"

#. Tag: phrase
#: getting-started.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kturtle; on a fresh start"
msgstr "&kturtle; na nov začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this Getting Started guide we assume that the language of the "
"&turtlescript; commands is English. You can change this language with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Script Language</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu. Be aware that the language you set here "
"for &kturtle; is the one you use to type the &turtlescript; commands, not "
"the language used by &kde; on your computer and used to display the "
"&kturtle; interface and menus."
msgstr ""
"V tem vodniku za začetek predvidevamo, da je jezik &turtlescript; ukazi so "
"angleški. Ta jezik lahko spremenite s podmenijem "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Skriptni jezik</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Zavedajte se, da jezik, ki ga tukaj nastavite za "
"&kturtle; je tisti, ki ga uporabljate za tipkanje &turtlescript; ukazov, ne "
"jezika, ki ga uporablja &kde; na vašem računalniku in se uporablja za prikaz "
"datoteke &kturtle; vmesnik in meniji."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "First steps with &turtlescript;: meet the Turtle!"
msgstr "Prvi koraki s &turtlescript;: spoznajte želvo!"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must have noticed the turtle in the middle of the canvas: you are just "
"about to learn how to control it using commands in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovo ste opazili želvo na sredini platna: pravkar se boste naučili, kako "
"jo upravljati z ukazi v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Turtle Moves"
msgstr "Premiki želve"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let us start by getting the turtle moving. Our turtle can do 3 types of "
"moves, (1) it can move forwards and backwards, (2) it can turn left and "
"right and (3) it can go (jump) directly to a position on the screen. Try "
"this for example:"
msgstr ""
"Začnimo s premikanjem želve. Naša želva lahko izvaja 3 vrste gibov, (1) "
"lahko se premika naprej in nazaj, (2) lahko se obrača levo in desno in (3) "
"lahko gre (skoči) neposredno na položaj na zaslonu. Poskusite to na primer:"

#. Tag: screen
#: getting-started.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 90"
msgstr ""
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 90"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type or copy-paste the code to the editor and execute it (using <link "
"linkend=\"run-execute\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice></link>) to see the result."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ali kopirajte in prilepite kodo v urejevalnik in jo izvedite (z "
"uporabo <link linkend=\"run-execute\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Zaženi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaženi</guimenuitem></menuchoice></link>), da vidite "
"rezultat."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you typed and executed the commands like above in the editor you might "
"have noticed one or more of the following things:"
msgstr ""
"Ko ste v urejevalnik vnesli in izvedli ukaze, kot je zgoraj, ste morda "
"opazili eno ali več od naslednjih stvari:"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That &mdash; after executing the commands &mdash; the turtle moves up, draws "
"a line, and then turns a quarter turn to the left. This because you have "
"used the <link linkend=\"forward\"><userinput>forward</userinput></link> and "
"the <link linkend=\"turnleft\"><userinput>turnleft</userinput></link> "
"commands."
msgstr ""
"ToTo &mdash; po izvedbi ukazov &mdash; želva se premakne navzgor, nariše "
"črto in se nato obrne za četrt obrata v levo. To je zato, ker ste uporabili "
"ukaza <link linkend=\"forward\"><userinput>naprej</userinput></link> in "
"<link linkend=\"turnleft\"><userinput>turnleft</userinput></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That the color of the code changed while you where typing it: this feature "
"is called <emphasis>intuitive highlighting</emphasis> &mdash; different "
"types of commands are highlighted differently. This makes reading large "
"blocks of code more easy."
msgstr ""
"Da se je barva kode spremenila, medtem ko ste jo vnašali: ta funkcija se "
"imenuje <emphasis>intuitivno označevanje</emphasis> &mdash; različne vrste "
"ukazov so različno označene. To olajša branje velikih blokov kode."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "That the turtle draws a thin black line."
msgstr "Da želva nariše tanko črno črto."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maybe you got an error message. This could simply mean two things: you could "
"have made a mistake while copying the commands, or you should still set the "
"correct language for the &turtlescript; commands (you can do that by "
"choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Script "
"Language</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu)."
msgstr ""
"Morda ste dobili sporočilo o napaki. To lahko preprosto pomeni dve stvari: "
"morda ste naredili napako pri kopiranju ukazov ali pa bi vseeno morali "
"nastaviti pravilen jezik za &turtlescript; ukaze (to lahko storite tako, da "
"izberete podmeni <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Skriptni jezik</guisubmenu></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will likely understand that <userinput>forward 100</userinput> "
"instructed the turtle to move forward leaving a line, and that "
"<userinput>turnleft 90</userinput> instructed the turtle to turn 90 "
"<glossterm linkend=\"degrees\">degrees</glossterm> to the left."
msgstr ""
"Verjetno boste razumeli, da je <userinput>forward 100</userinput> ukazal "
"želvi, naj se premakne naprej zapusti črto, in da je <userinput>turnleft 90</"
"userinput> ukazal želvi, naj se obrne za 90 <glossterm linkend=\"degrees"
"\">stopinj </glossterm> na levo."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please see the following links to the reference manual for a complete "
"explanation of the new commands: <link linkend=\"forward"
"\"><userinput>forward</userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"backward"
"\"><userinput>backward</userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"turnleft"
"\"><userinput>turnleft</userinput></link>, and <link linkend=\"turnright"
"\"><userinput>turnright</userinput></link>."
msgstr ""
"Za popolno razlago novih ukazov si oglejte naslednje povezave do "
"referenčnega priročnika: <link linkend=\"forward\"><userinput>naprej</"
"userinput></link>, <link linkend=\"backward\"><userinput> nazaj</userinput></"
"link>, <link linkend=\"turnleft\"><userinput>zavijte levo</userinput></link> "
"in <link linkend=\"turnright\"><userinput>zavijte desno</userinput></link>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "More examples"
msgstr "Več primerov"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first example was very simple, so let us go on!"
msgstr "Prvi primer je bil zelo preprost, zato pojdimo naprej!"

#. Tag: screen
#: getting-started.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"reset\n"
"\n"
"canvassize 200,200\n"
"canvascolor 0,0,0\n"
"pencolor 255,0,0\n"
"penwidth 5\n"
"\n"
"go 20,20\n"
"direction 135\n"
"\n"
"forward 200\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 141\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 45\n"
"\n"
"go 40,100"
msgstr ""
"reset\n"
"\n"
"canvassize 200,200\n"
"canvascolor 0,0,0\n"
"pencolor 255,0,0\n"
"penwidth 5\n"
"\n"
"go 20,20\n"
"direction 135\n"
"\n"
"forward 200\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 141\n"
"turnleft 135\n"
"forward 100\n"
"turnleft 45\n"
"\n"
"go 40,100"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Again you can type or copy-paste the code to the editor or open the "
"<filename>arrow</filename> example in the <guimenu>Examples</guimenu> "
"submenu and execute it (using <link linkend=\"run-execute"
"\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice></link>) to see the result. In the next examples you are expected "
"to know the drill."
msgstr ""
"Spet lahko vtipkate ali kopirate in prilepite kodo v urejevalnik ali odprete "
"primer <filename>puščice</filename> v podmeniju <guimenu>Primeri</guimenu> "
"in jo izvedete (z uporabo <link linkend=\"run-execute\" "
"><menuchoice><guimenu>Zaženi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaženi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice></link>), da vidite rezultat. V naslednjih primerih se pričakuje, "
"da poznate vajo."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might have noticed that this second example uses a lot more code. You "
"have also seen a couple of new commands. Here a short explanation of all the "
"new commands:"
msgstr ""
"Morda ste opazili, da ta drugi primer uporablja veliko več kode. Videli ste "
"tudi nekaj novih ukazov. Tukaj je kratka razlaga vseh novih ukazov:"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After a <userinput>reset</userinput> command everything is like is was when "
"you had just started &kturtle;."
msgstr ""
"Po ukazu <userinput>reset</userinput> je vse tako, kot je bilo, ko ste "
"pravkar zagnali &kturtle;."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>canvassize 200,200</userinput> sets the canvas width and height "
"to 200 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm>. The width and the "
"height are equal, so the canvas will be a square."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>canvassize 200,200</userinput> nastavi širino in višino platna na "
"200 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pikslov</glossterm>. Širina in višina sta "
"enaki, zato bo platno kvadrat."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>canvascolor 0,0,0</userinput> makes the canvas black. "
"<userinput>0,0,0</userinput> is a <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-"
"combination</glossterm> where all values are set to <userinput>0</"
"userinput>, which results in black."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>canvascolor 0,0,0</userinput> naredi platno črno. "
"<userinput>0,0,0</userinput> je <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-kombinacija</"
"glossterm>, kjer so vse vrednosti nastavljene na <userinput>0</userinput>, "
"kar povzroči črno barvo."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>pencolor 255,0,0</userinput> sets the color of the pen to red. "
"<userinput>255,0,0</userinput> is a <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-"
"combination</glossterm> where only the red value is set to <userinput>255</"
"userinput> (fully on) while the others (green and blue) are set to "
"<userinput>0</userinput> (fully off). This results in a bright shade of red."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>pencolor 255,0,0</userinput> nastavi barvo peresa na rdečo. "
"<userinput>255,0,0</userinput> je <glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-"
"kombinacija</glossterm>, kjer je samo rdeča vrednost nastavljena na "
"<userinput>255</userinput> (popolnoma vključena), medtem ko druge (zelena in "
"modra) so nastavljene na <userinput>0</userinput> (popolnoma izklopljene). "
"Posledica tega je svetel odtenek rdeče."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not understand the color values, be sure to read the glossary on "
"<glossterm linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-combination</glossterm>."
msgstr ""
"Če ne razumete barvnih vrednosti, obvezno preberite glosar o <glossterm "
"linkend=\"rgb\">RGB-kombinaciji</glossterm>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>penwidth 5</userinput> sets the width (the size) of the pen to "
"<userinput>5</userinput> <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm>. "
"From now on every line the turtle draw will have a thickness of "
"<userinput>5</userinput>, until we change the <userinput>penwidth</"
"userinput> to something else."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>penwidth 5</userinput> nastavi širino (velikost) peresa na "
"<userinput>5</userinput> <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pikslov</glossterm>. "
"Od zdaj naprej bo imela vsaka črta, ki jo nariše želva, debelino "
"<userinput>5</userinput>, dokler <userinput>širine peresa</userinput> ne "
"spremenimo v nekaj drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>go 20,20</userinput> commands the turtle to go to a certain place "
"on the canvas. Counted from the upper left corner, this place is 20 "
"<glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm> across from the left, and "
"20 <glossterm linkend=\"pixels\">pixels</glossterm> down from the top of the "
"canvas. Note that using the <userinput>go</userinput> command the turtle "
"will not draw a line."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>go 20,20</userinput> ukaže želvi, naj gre na določeno mesto na "
"platnu. Če štejemo od zgornjega levega kota, je to mesto 20 <glossterm "
"linkend=\"pixels\">pikslov</glossterm> čez levo in 20 <glossterm linkend="
"\"pixels\">pikslov</glossterm> navzdol od vrha platno. Upoštevajte, da z "
"ukazom <userinput>go</userinput> želva ne bo narisala črte."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>direction 135</userinput> set the turtle's direction. The "
"<userinput>turnleft</userinput> and <userinput>turnright</userinput> "
"commands change the turtle's angle starting from its current direction. The "
"<userinput>direction</userinput> command changes the turtle's angle from "
"zero, and thus is not relative to the turtle previous direction."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>direction 135</userinput> nastavi smer želve. Ukaza "
"<userinput>turnleft</userinput> in <userinput>turnright</userinput> "
"spremenita kot želve, začenši z njeno trenutno smerjo. Ukaz "
"<userinput>direction</userinput> spremeni kot želve iz nič in tako ni "
"relativen glede na prejšnjo smer želve."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the <userinput>direction</userinput> command a lot of "
"<userinput>forward</userinput> and <userinput>turnleft</userinput> commands "
"follow. These command do the actual drawing."
msgstr ""
"Po ukazu <userinput>direction</userinput> sledi veliko ukazov "
"<userinput>forward</userinput> in <userinput>turnleft</userinput>. Ti ukazi "
"naredijo dejansko risanje."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At last another <userinput>go</userinput> command is used to move the turtle "
"aside."
msgstr ""
"Končno se uporabi še en ukaz <userinput>go</userinput> za premik želve na "
"stran."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure you follow the links to the reference. The reference explains each "
"command more thoroughly."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da sledite povezavam do reference. Referenca podrobneje "
"pojasnjuje vsak ukaz."
